question.text: Berapa jumlah minimum untuk withdrawal dan apakah panduan kategori pertaruhan 4D, 3D, dan 2D?
variations: Berapa minimum jumlah yang diperlukan untuk withdraw dan bagaimana kategori 4D, 3D, 2D ditentukan?
Apa syarat minimum untuk withdrawal dan panduan untuk pertaruhan 4D, 3D, 2D?
Berapakah jumlah minimum withdraw dan bagaimana cara menentukan 3D dan 2D daripada 4D?

languages.en: "What is the minimum amount required for withdrawal and what are the betting guidelines for 4D, 3D, and 2D?"
languages.ms: "Berapa jumlah minimum untuk withdrawal dan apakah panduan kategori pertaruhan 4D, 3D, dan 2D?"
languages.cn: "取款的最低金额是多少，以及4D、3D和2D的投注指南是什么？"

detailed.en:
"Hi boss, the current minimum withdrawal amount is RM30. Additionally, here are the guidelines for the betting categories:

• 4D (Tegak Sahaja): Includes prizes 4A (1st), 4B (2nd), 4C (3rd), 4D (Special), and 4E (Consolation).

• 3D: Based on the last three digits of the 4D number, with categories such as 3A (1st), 3B (2nd), 3C (3rd), 3D (Special, multiplied by 10), 3E (Consolation, multiplied by 10), and 3N covering all prizes.

• 2D: Based on the last two digits of the 4D number, with categories 2A (1st), 2B (2nd), 2C (3rd), 2D (Special, multiplied by 10), 2E (Consolation, multiplied by 10), and 2N covering all prizes.

For 3D and 2D, only the ending digits of the 4D number are used (e.g., if 4D = 1234, then 3D = 234 and 2D = 34)."
detailed.ms:
"Hi boss, jumlah minimum untuk withdrawal adalah RM30. Berikut juga panduan untuk kategori pertaruhan:

• 4D (Tegak Sahaja): Termasuk hadiah 4A (1st), 4B (2nd), 4C (3rd), 4D (Special) dan 4E (Consolation).

• 3D: Berdasarkan tiga digit terakhir nombor 4D, dengan kategori seperti 3A (1st), 3B (2nd), 3C (3rd), 3D (Special, X10), 3E (Consolation, X10) dan 3N merangkumi semua hadiah.

• 2D: Berdasarkan dua digit terakhir nombor 4D, dengan kategori 2A (1st), 2B (2nd), 2C (3rd), 2D (Special, X10), 2E (Consolation, X10) dan 2N merangkumi semua hadiah.

Untuk 3D dan 2D, hanya digit terakhir nombor 4D yang digunakan (contoh: jika 4D = 1234, maka 3D = 234 dan 2D = 34)."
detailed.cn:
"嗨，老板，当前的最低取款金额是RM30。以下是4D、3D和2D投注的指南：

• 4D（竖式）：包括4A（一等奖）、4B（二等奖）、4C（三等奖）、4D（特别奖）和4E（安慰奖）。

• 3D：基于4D号码的后三位，分类包括3A（一等）、3B（二等）、3C（三等）、3D（特别奖，X10）、3E（安慰奖，X10）以及涵盖所有奖项的3N。

• 2D：基于4D号码的后两位，分类包括2A（一等）、2B（二等）、2C（三等）、2D（特别奖，X10）、2E（安慰奖，X10）以及涵盖所有奖项的2N。

对于3D和2D，只取4D号码的末尾数字（例如：如果4D = 1234，则3D = 234，2D = 34）。"

question.text: What do the abbreviations BT, BH, and RV mean in the context of betting?
variations: BT BH RV apa mksud dia
Sama mcm box jg ke?

languages.en: What do the abbreviations BT, BH, and RV mean in the context of betting?
languages.ms: BT BH RV apa mksud dia

detailed.en: In the context of 4D betting, the abbreviations mean the following: RV (Round Return – Reverse Balik) refers to a number that is completely reversed (e.g., 1234 becomes 4321). BH (Pao Kepala – First Digit Fixed) means the first digit remains the same while the others can change (e.g., 1223 can become 1232 or 1322). BT (Pao Ekor – Last Digit Fixed) indicates that the last digit does not change while the others can be rearranged (e.g., 1223 can become 2123 or 2213). Additionally, IBOX is similar to BOX but with a fixed price of RM1, and the payout is divided according to the number of combinations. BOX is a bet that includes all possible combinations (the arrangement of digits can change).
detailed.ms: Dalam konteks pertaruhan 4D, singkatan ini bermaksud: RV (Round Return – Reverse Balik) merujuk kepada nombor yang dibalik sepenuhnya (contohnya, 1234 menjadi 4321). BH (Pao Kepala – Nombor Pertama Tak Bergerak) bermaksud digit pertama kekal sama manakala yang lain boleh berubah (contohnya, 1223 boleh jadi 1232 atau 1322). BT (Pao Ekor – Nombor Akhir Tak Bergerak) menunjukkan bahawa digit terakhir tidak berubah manakala yang lain boleh disusun semula (contohnya, 1223 boleh jadi 2123 atau 2213). Selain itu, IBOX adalah sama seperti BOX tetapi dengan harga tetap RM1, dan pembayaran dibahagikan mengikut bilangan kombinasi. BOX adalah pertaruhan yang merangkumi semua kemungkinan kombinasi (susunan digit boleh berubah).

detailed.en: Currently, there is no bonus angpau available for old IDs. If there are any new promotions in the future, we will update them directly in the app. Please be patient, as opportunities can arise at any time!
detailed.ms: Buat masa sekarang memang tiada bonus angpau untuk ID lama. Kalau ada promo baru nanti, kami akan update terus dalam app. Sabar sikit, rezeki boleh datang bila-bila masa!

question.text: Why hasn't my claim for the transaction at 10.25 PM been processed yet?
variations: Why is my 10.25 PM claim still not approved?
What is the status of my 10.25 PM transaction claim?

languages.en: Why hasn't my claim for the transaction at 10.25 PM been processed yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa claim saya untuk transaksi pada 10.25 PM belum diproses?

detailed.en: If your claim for the transaction at 10.25 PM has not been processed yet, it may be due to a delay in the system. Please wait for about 10 more minutes. If there is still no update, send a screenshot of your transaction receipt so I can check further.
detailed.ms: Jika claim anda untuk transaksi pada 10.25 PM belum diproses, mungkin ada kelewatan dalam sistem. Mohon tunggu sekitar 10 minit lagi. Jika selepas itu masih tiada kemasukan, sila hantar screenshot resit transaksi untuk saya semak dengan lebih lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my credit balance suddenly goes to zero after topping up?
variations: Why is my credit balance empty?
What happens if my credit doesn't show up after a top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if my credit balance suddenly goes to zero after topping up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika baki kredit saya tiba-tiba kosong selepas top-up?

detailed.en: If you have topped up RM50 but the credit hasn't appeared, it usually takes 3 to 10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and you still haven't received it, please send the complete transaction receipt via live chat for further inspection. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika kamu sudah top-up RM50 tetapi kredit belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3 hingga 10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih belum diterima, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: I haven't received my credit yet. Can you help me with this issue?
variations: Boss credit belum masuk

languages.en: I haven't received my credit yet. Can you help me with this issue?
languages.ms: Boss credit belum masuk

detailed.en: To top up, please upload the receipt in the Topup section of the JOKER app. Do not send it here (live chat) as the system will only check receipts submitted on the top-up page. After uploading, wait for 3–10 minutes for the system to process. If there are any issues, please send a screenshot of the transaction and select the correct bank, then contact us again.
detailed.ms: Untuk topup, resit hanya perlu upload di bahagian Topup dalam app JOKER sahaja ya. Jangan hantar di sini (livechat) sebab sistem hanya akan semak resit yang dihantar di halaman topup. Lepas upload, tunggu 3–10 minit untuk sistem proses. Kalau ada masalah, boleh hantar screenshot transaksi + pilih bank yang betul, dan roger kami semula ya boss.

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been received after topping up?
variations: What to do if the credit hasn't arrived?
How long does it take for the credit to show up?

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been received after topping up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya belum diterima selepas top up?
languages.cn: 如果我充值后信用没有到账，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you have topped up and the credit has not been received, please wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If the funds still do not appear, send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the credit is still not in, please send a screenshot of the transaction receipt for immediate checking.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top up dan kredit belum diterima, sila tunggu dalam 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika dana masih belum masuk, hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan kredit masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan layar resit transaksi untuk semakan segera.
detailed.cn: 如果您已经充值但信用未到账，请等待3-10分钟以进行确认。如果资金仍未出现，请通过实时聊天发送收据以获得进一步帮助。如果超过10分钟信用仍未到账，请发送交易收据的截图以便立即检查。

question.text: Saya ingin tahu tentang status deposit RM350 yang masih pending dan juga mengenai pembelian nombor yang saya takut tidak sempat.
variations: Deposit RM350 saya masih pending.
Saya nak beli nombor, takut tak sempat.

languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu tentang status deposit RM350 yang masih pending dan juga mengenai pembelian nombor yang saya takut tidak sempat.

detailed.en: If your RM350 deposit is still pending, it usually takes between 3 to 10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction receipt you uploaded. If it hasn't been credited after that, you can send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. If you want to buy a number for tonight's draw, make sure your funds are credited. If not, I recommend contacting live chat for immediate help. They can assist you faster.
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM350 anda masih pending, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak semula resit transaksi yang telah dimuat naik. Jika masih belum dikredit selepas itu, anda boleh hantarkan resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika anda ingin beli nombor untuk cabutan malam ini, pastikan dana anda sudah dikredit. Jika masih belum, saya sarankan anda hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: Saya ingin tahu tentang proses deposit dan mengapa point belum masuk selepas deposit.
variations: Kenapa point saya belum masuk?
Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika point tidak muncul selepas deposit?

languages.en: I want to know about the deposit process and why the points haven't been credited after the deposit.
languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu tentang proses deposit dan mengapa point belum masuk selepas deposit.

detailed.en: If the points haven't been credited after the deposit, it usually takes time to process. Please wait around 10 minutes. If they still don't appear, you can contact live chat with your transaction details for further assistance. Hope it settles quickly!
detailed.ms: Kalau point belum masuk selepas deposit, biasanya ia mengambil masa untuk diproses. Sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit. Kalau masih tak muncul, boleh hubungi live chat dengan maklumat transaksi untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga cepat settle, boss!

question.text: What happened to the Sandakan draw? Why has it not been announced yet?

languages.en: What happened to the Sandakan draw? Why has it not been announced yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang terjadi dengan undian Sandakan? Kenapa ia belum diumumkan?
languages.cn: Sandakan抽奖发生了什么？为什么还没有宣布？

detailed.en: If the Sandakan results have not been released yet, don't worry. Usually, the results and prizes will still be awarded to the winners. The estimated time for the results is as follows: Sandakan 3PM → 4:00PM - 4:30PM and Sandakan 7PM → 8:00PM - 8:30PM. Sometimes the results may be a bit late, but all prizes will be credited as usual. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika keputusan Sandakan belum dikeluarkan, jangan risau. Biasanya keputusan dan hadiah tetap akan diberikan kepada pemenang. Waktu anggaran untuk keputusan adalah seperti berikut: Sandakan 3PM → 4:00PM - 4:30PM dan Sandakan 7PM → 8:00PM - 8:30PM. Kadang-kadang keputusan mungkin sedikit lewat, tetapi semua hadiah akan dikreditkan seperti biasa. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!
detailed.cn: 如果Sandakan的结果还没有发布，请不要担心。通常，结果和奖品仍会颁发给获胜者。结果的预计时间如下：Sandakan 3PM → 4:00PM - 4:30PM 和 Sandakan 7PM → 8:00PM - 8:30PM。有时结果可能会稍晚，但所有奖品将照常发放。感谢您的耐心等待！

question.text: I have not received my points from the IBG transfer yet. Can you help me check the status?
variations: What is the status of my IBG transfer?
Why haven't my points from the IBG transfer been credited yet?

languages.en: I have not received my points from the IBG transfer yet. Can you help me check the status?
languages.ms: Saya belum menerima mata dari pemindahan IBG lagi. Bolehkah anda membantu saya menyemak status?

detailed.en: If the transaction using IBG has not been processed yet, it usually takes 1-3 working days for the bank to process it. If after 3 days it still hasn't been credited, you should check with the bank for the transaction status. If you need further assistance, please send the transaction receipt to live chat, and we will help you check.
detailed.ms: Jika transaksi menggunakan IBG, memang ambil masa 1-3 hari bekerja untuk diproses oleh bank. Jika selepas 3 hari masih belum masuk, boleh semak dengan bank untuk status transaksi. Jika perlu bantuan lanjut, hantar resit transaksi ke live chat, dan kami akan bantu semak.

detailed.ms: Ya, itu adalah ID JOKER yang betul. Pastikan anda menggunakannya untuk semua transaksi. Jika ada masalah, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What time does the mask number draw take place and when will the winnings be credited to my wallet?
variations: bosku duit kena nombor mask pukul berapa
What time is the mask number draw?

languages.en: What time does the mask number draw take place and when will the winnings be credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: bosku duit kena nombor mask pukul berapa

detailed.en: The mask number draw usually takes place at 9:00 PM. Ensure you purchase your number before the betting closes at 7:00 PM. If you win, the winnings will typically be credited to your wallet within 30 minutes after the results are announced. In your case, the RM40 winnings have already been credited to your wallet. You can check it in Wallet → Transaction History.
detailed.ms: Cabutan nombor mask biasanya berlangsung pada pukul 9:00 PM. Pastikan anda membeli nombor sebelum waktu tutup pertaruhan pada pukul 7:00 PM. Jika anda menang, duit kemenangan biasanya akan dimasukkan ke dalam wallet anda dalam masa 30 minit selepas keputusan diumumkan. Dalam kes anda, duit RM40 sudah pun dimasukkan ke dalam wallet anda. Anda boleh semak di Wallet → Transaction History.

detailed.ms: Kalau guna Fast Payment (eWallet), mohon tunggu dalam 10 minit ya, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 10 minit, boss boleh roger kami semula untuk semakan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi, kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: I usually top up on KZ Furniture account, but I noticed the bank account is different this time. What should I do?
variations: I noticed the bank account is different when I topped up.
What should I do if the bank account for my top-up is not the same?

languages.en: I usually top up on KZ Furniture account, but I noticed the bank account is different this time. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya biasanya top-up pada akaun KZ Furniture, tetapi saya perasan akaun bank berbeza kali ini. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: Please always check the list of bank accounts shown in the app before making any transfer. Don’t use old accounts or ones saved in your 'favourites' without confirming. If you want to save as favourite, make sure it’s the current active account from the app. If the transfer goes to the wrong account, the process will be delayed.
detailed.ms: Sila sentiasa semak senarai akaun bank yang ditunjukkan dalam aplikasi sebelum membuat sebarang pemindahan. Jangan gunakan akaun lama atau yang disimpan dalam 'kegemaran' tanpa mengesahkan. Jika anda ingin menyimpan sebagai kegemaran, pastikan ia adalah akaun aktif semasa dari aplikasi. Jika pemindahan pergi ke akaun yang salah, proses akan ditangguhkan.

question.text: I have topped up my wallet, but the amount has not been credited yet. What should I do?
variations: I have topped up but it hasn't appeared in my wallet.
My top-up is not showing in my wallet.

languages.en: I have topped up my wallet, but the amount has not been credited yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya sudah top-up tetapi belum masuk ke dalam wallet.

detailed.en: If you have topped up but the amount hasn't appeared in your wallet, please follow these steps: 1️⃣ Open the JOKER app 2️⃣ Tap on the Wallet icon → Go to Transaction History 3️⃣ Check the status of your top-up (Pending / Approved). If the status is Pending, it means it's still processing (please wait 3–10 minutes). If there is no status or it has been more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your receipt here, and I will assist you further.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up tetapi jumlahnya belum muncul dalam wallet, sila ikut langkah ini: 1️⃣ Buka aplikasi JOKER 2️⃣ Tekan ikon Wallet → Pergi ke Transaction History 3️⃣ Semak status topup (Pending / Approved). Jika status Pending, ia bermakna ia masih dalam proses (tunggu 3–10 minit). Jika tiada status atau sudah lebih 10 minit, hantarkan screenshot resit ke sini, dan saya akan bantu anda lanjut.

question.text: I have topped up my account, but the credit has not been added yet. What should I do?
variations: boss blm ada masuk ya
dari tadi topup tu boss, tapi credit tak masuk lagi

languages.en: I have topped up my account, but the credit has not been added yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah menambah nilai akaun saya, tetapi kredit belum ditambahkan lagi. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
languages.cn: 我已经充值了我的账户，但信用尚未添加。我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If the credit has not been added after topping up, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please ensure that you have uploaded the transaction receipt correctly. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the credit is still not added, please send the complete transaction receipt to us via live chat for further verification. We will assist you as soon as possible! 😊
detailed.ms: Jika kredit belum masuk selepas top-up, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Pastikan juga anda telah memuat naik resit transaksi dengan betul. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih tiada kredit, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap kepada kami melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin! 😊
detailed.cn: 如果充值后信用尚未添加，通常需要3-10分钟进行处理。请确保您已正确上传交易收据。如果超过10分钟仍未添加信用，请通过在线聊天将完整的交易收据发送给我们以进行进一步验证。我们会尽快协助您！😊

question.text: Why is my money taking so long to be credited to my account after I made a top-up?
variations: Lambat duit masuk.
Dah lebih 5 minit, kenapa duit tak masuk?

languages.en: Why is my money taking so long to be credited to my account after I made a top-up?
languages.ms: Kenapa duit saya lambat masuk selepas saya buat topup?

detailed.en: Sometimes, the processing of winnings can be slow. Typically, it should be credited within 5 to 30 minutes. If the money hasn't arrived after that period, you can check the transaction status in the app. If there are still issues, please contact customer support via live chat for further assistance. If the top-up is still pending, please be patient as the system is processing it. After uploading the receipt, the top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't arrived, you can send the receipt to live chat for immediate review.
detailed.ms: Kadang-kadang pemprosesan kemenangan boleh jadi lambat. Biasanya, ia akan masuk dalam 5 hingga 30 minit. Jika duit masih tak masuk selepas tempoh tu, boleh cuba semak status transaksi dalam aplikasi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up money has not been credited to my account after uploading the receipt?
variations: What to do if my top-up is not successful?
How can I check my top-up status?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up money has not been credited to my account after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika duit top-up saya tidak masuk selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If the money has not been credited, check the following: 1. Ensure you have uploaded the correct receipt. 2. Verify the bank account used for payment. 3. Check the transaction record in the app. If the issue persists, contact customer support via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika duit tidak masuk, semak beberapa perkara ini: 1. Pastikan anda telah muat naik resit yang betul. 2. Semak akaun bank yang digunakan untuk pembayaran. 3. Lihat rekod transaksi dalam aplikasi. Jika masih tidak ada, boleh hubungi sokongan pelanggan melalui sembang langsung untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Can you confirm the status of my top-up and whether my receipt has been processed?
variations: saya nk kepastian

languages.en: Can you confirm the status of my top-up and whether my receipt has been processed?
languages.ms: saya nk kepastian

detailed.en: You can check the status of your top-up in the 'Wallet' → 'Transaction History'. If the system shows 'Pending', it means your receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait 3-10 minutes for the top-up process to complete. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, you can send your receipt to live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Status topup boleh disemak di 'Wallet' → 'Transaction History'. Jika sistem tunjuk 'Pending', maksudnya resit anda sudah berjaya diupload. Sila tunggu 3-10 minit untuk proses topup selesai. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: How can I check the ID for my transaction?

languages.en: How can I check the ID for my transaction?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menyemak ID untuk transaksi saya?

detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah transfer RM350 tetapi tidak meletakkan nombor rujukan, kami mungkin tidak dapat mengesahkan transaksi dengan cepat. Lain kali, pastikan untuk menulis ID JOKER dalam 'Recipient Reference' setiap kali buat transfer. Kerjasama anda sangat kami hargai! Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang perlu dibantu, beritahu saja ya!
detailed.cn: 如果您已经转账RM350但没有填写参考号码，我们可能无法快速确认交易。下次，请确保在每次转账时在“收件人参考”中写下ID JOKER。我们非常感谢您的合作！如果您需要其他帮助，请告诉我！

question.text: Kenapa duit saya belum masuk setelah melakukan transaksi?
variations: Duit saya belum masuk, apa yang perlu saya buat?
Saya sudah transfer tetapi duit belum dikreditkan, kenapa?

languages.en: Why hasn't my money been credited after the transaction?
languages.ms: Kenapa duit saya belum masuk setelah melakukan transaksi?

detailed.en: If you have transferred RM350 but did not include the reference number, that might be the reason why the money hasn't been credited. The reference number is very important for verification. Next time, make sure to include the ID JOKER in the 'Recipient Reference' so we can verify quickly. Thank you for your cooperation, and may you always have good fortune!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah transfer RM350 tetapi tidak letak nombor rujukan, itu mungkin sebabnya duit belum masuk. Nombor rujukan sangat penting untuk pengesahan. Lain kali, pastikan untuk letak ID JOKER dalam 'Recipient Reference' supaya kami boleh sahkan dengan cepat. Terima kasih atas kerjasama anda, dan semoga HUAT selalu!

question.text: Why hasn't my banking transaction been credited yet?
variations: dah banking Belum masuk lagi

languages.en: Why hasn't my banking transaction been credited yet?
languages.ms: dah banking Belum masuk lagi

detailed.en: If the funds have not been credited after the expected time, please send your transaction details via live chat so we can check it immediately. Additionally, ensure that the receipt has been uploaded to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still hasn't been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Jika wang masih belum masuk selepas jangka masa yang dijangka, sila hantarkan butiran transaksi anda melalui live chat supaya kami dapat semak dengan segera. Selain itu, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Lepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Can you help me check the status of my transaction or game?
variations: boleh tolong check x
ada kne ka

languages.en: Can you help me check the status of my transaction or game?
languages.ms: Boleh tolong semak status transaksi atau permainan saya?

detailed.en: If you have topped up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) for RM60 but it hasn't reflected yet, it usually takes 1-3 minutes to process. If it has been more than 3 minutes and it still hasn't appeared, please check the transaction in the TNG app first. If there is still no update, send us the FPX transaction receipt via live chat for further verification. We will assist in processing it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) sebanyak RM60 tetapi belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 1-3 minit untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih dari 3 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi TNG terlebih dahulu. Jika masih tiada, hantarkan resit transaksi FPX kepada kami melalui live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu proses secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my RM20 transfer to CIMB has not been received after a long wait?
variations: Why hasn't my RM20 transfer been received yet?
What are the reasons for my RM20 transfer delay?

languages.en: What should I do if my RM20 transfer to CIMB has not been received after a long wait?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan RM20 saya ke CIMB belum diterima selepas menunggu lama?

detailed.en: If you have transferred RM20 to CIMB and it has not been received after more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the transaction receipt. We will check and assist you as soon as possible. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memindahkan RM20 ke CIMB dan ia belum diterima selepas lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit transaksi. Kami akan semak dan bantu anda secepat mungkin. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: Why hasn't my winning credit been credited yet?
variations: Kenapa kredit kemenangan saya belum masuk?
Bila kredit kemenangan saya akan diterima?

languages.en: Why hasn't my winning credit been credited yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa kredit kemenangan saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If the winning credit hasn't been credited yet, there might be a slight delay. Please wait a moment, usually it will be credited within 30 minutes. If you still haven't received it, you can check with support for confirmation. Don't worry, good fortune is on the way!
detailed.ms: Jika kredit kemenangan belum masuk, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan. Sila tunggu sekejap, biasanya ia akan masuk dalam masa 30 minit. Jika masih belum dapat, boleh check dengan support untuk pengesahan. Jangan risau, rezeki tengah jalan!

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal has not yet been credited to my bank account?
variations: Why hasn't my withdrawal arrived in my bank?
What are the reasons for a delay in my bank withdrawal?

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal has not yet been credited to my bank account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya belum dikreditkan ke akaun bank saya?

detailed.en: If you have made a withdrawal and it has not yet arrived in your bank account, please check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and you still have not received it, you can send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it is still not credited, please send the transaction details to live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat pengeluaran dan ia belum tiba di akaun bank anda, sila semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan anda masih belum menerimanya, anda boleh menghantar butiran transaksi ke sembang langsung untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam dompet anda untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar butiran transaksi ke sembang langsung untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Saya ingin tahu mengapa pengeluaran RM400 saya tidak masuk ke dalam akaun dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan mengenainya.
variations: Kenapa RM400 saya tidak masuk?
Apa yang perlu saya buat jika pengeluaran tidak masuk?
Bagaimana untuk menyemak status pengeluaran RM400 saya?

languages.en: I want to know why my withdrawal of RM400 has not entered my account and what I should do about it.
languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu mengapa pengeluaran RM400 saya tidak masuk ke dalam akaun dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan mengenainya.

detailed.en: If the RM400 withdrawal has not entered your account after more than 30 minutes, please check the transaction status in the app. If it still does not appear, provide me with the transaction details such as the time and date of the withdrawal so I can assist you further. If the bank is undergoing maintenance, usually the funds will be credited back to your wallet. If the RM400 has not entered at all, I recommend contacting customer support through the live chat in the app for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran RM400 tu belum masuk ke dalam akaun selepas lebih dari 30 minit, sila semak status transaksi dalam aplikasi. Jika masih tidak ada, berikan saya butiran transaksi seperti masa dan tarikh pengeluaran supaya saya boleh bantu semak dengan lebih tepat. Jika bank sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, biasanya dana akan dikreditkan semula ke dalam wallet anda. Jika RM400 tu memang tidak masuk langsung, saya syorkan untuk hubungi sokongan pelanggan melalui sembang langsung dalam aplikasi untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I have withdrawn money, but it hasn't appeared in my bank account yet. What should I do?

languages.en: I have withdrawn money, but it hasn't appeared in my bank account yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah mengeluarkan duit, tetapi ia belum muncul dalam akaun bank saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
languages.cn: 我已经提取了钱，但它还没有出现在我的银行账户中。我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If the withdrawal has been more than 30 minutes and the money has not yet appeared, please check the transaction status in the app. If it still hasn't appeared, you can send us the transaction details via live chat for immediate checking. We will help ensure everything goes smoothly for you. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran sudah lebih dari 30 minit tetapi belum masuk, sila semak status transaksi dalam aplikasi ya. Jika masih tiada, boleh hantar butiran transaksi kepada kami melalui sembang langsung untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu pastikan semuanya berjalan lancar untuk anda. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!
detailed.cn: 如果提款超过30分钟但尚未到账，请在应用程序中检查交易状态。如果仍然没有，您可以通过实时聊天向我们发送交易详细信息以进行即时检查。我们将帮助确保一切顺利进行。感谢您的耐心等待！

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure the transaction is confirmed?
variations: What steps do I need to take after topping up?
How can I confirm my top-up transaction?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure the transaction is confirmed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai untuk memastikan transaksi disahkan?
languages.cn: 我在充值后应该做什么以确保交易被确认？

detailed.en: Make sure you have uploaded the transaction receipt in the top-up section of the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, send a clear screenshot via live chat for immediate assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit transaksi dalam bahagian top-up di aplikasi. Tunggu dalam 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum dikreditkan, hantar tangkapan skrin yang jelas melalui sembang langsung untuk bantuan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!
detailed.cn: 确保您已在应用程序的充值部分上传了交易收据。等待1-10分钟以便系统确认交易。如果在10分钟后仍未入账，请通过在线聊天发送清晰的屏幕截图以获得即时帮助。感谢您的耐心等待！

question.text: I made a mistake in the amount I wrote, how can I correct it?
variations: I wrote the wrong amount, what should I do?
How do I fix the amount I submitted?

languages.en: I made a mistake in the amount I wrote, how can I correct it?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat kesilapan dalam jumlah yang saya tulis, bagaimana saya boleh membetulkannya?
languages.cn: 我写的金额有误，我该如何更正？

detailed.en: Please re-upload the document and ensure that the amount is written as RM 20.
detailed.ms: Sila muat naik semula dokumen dan pastikan jumlah ditulis sebagai RM 20.
detailed.cn: 请重新上传文件，并确保金额写为RM 20。

question.text: What should I do if I made a mistake while entering my JOKER ID during an online transfer?
variations: What if I entered the wrong JOKER ID?
How can I correct a mistake in my JOKER ID for a transfer?

languages.en: What should I do if I made a mistake while entering my JOKER ID during an online transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya membuat kesilapan semasa memasukkan ID JOKER saya semasa pemindahan dalam talian?

detailed.en: If you have made a payment but there was an error, ensure that the amount entered matches your receipt. If there are further issues, try restarting the JOKER application and attempt the withdrawal again. Contact us via live chat if the problem persists.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat pembayaran tetapi terdapat kesilapan, pastikan jumlah yang dimasukkan sepadan dengan resit anda. Jika ada masalah lanjut, cuba mulakan semula aplikasi JOKER dan cuba lagi untuk pengeluaran. Hubungi kami melalui live chat jika masalah berterusan.

question.text: I mistakenly uploaded the wrong receipt for a top-up of RM50. How can I correct this?
variations: topup 50 tu sy silap msk gmbr td punya

languages.en: I mistakenly uploaded the wrong receipt for a top-up of RM50. How can I correct this?
languages.ms: topup 50 tu sy silap msk gmbr td punya

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the wrong receipt for the RM50 top-up, you can re-upload the correct receipt with the accurate amount. Make sure the receipt includes the JOKER ID. After that, the system will process it within 3-10 minutes. If you still do not see it in your account, you can contact us with a screenshot of the receipt for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Kalau boss dah masukkan gambar resit yang salah untuk top-up RM50 tu, boleh muat naik semula resit yang betul dengan amaun yang tepat. Pastikan resit tu ada JOKER ID. Lepas tu, sistem akan proses dalam 3-10 minit. Kalau masih tak nampak dalam akaun, boleh hubungi kami dengan tangkapan skrin resit untuk bantuan lanjut.

languages.cn: 你诚实吗？我花了超过11,000，但赢得很少……我玩是因为支持你，但我非常失望，直到我感到精疲力竭。

Is there a way to recover the RM200 I sent to the wrong place?

languages.en: I mistakenly transferred RM200 to the wrong account and would like to know if I can get it refunded.
languages.ms: Saya tertransfer RM200 ke tempat yang salah dan ingin tahu jika saya boleh dapatkan semula.

detailed.en: Hi boss, if you have transferred RM200 to the wrong place, I'm sorry, but we cannot refund it. 😔 What you can do is use the remaining balance to play and try to win it back. You need to win at least 30% of your capital before you can make a withdrawal. For example, if you transferred RM200, you need to win RM60 first before you can withdraw RM260. I hope you have good luck and win big! If you have any other questions, feel free to ask in the live chat! 😊🙏
detailed.ms: Hi boss, kalau dah tertransfer RM200 ke tempat yang salah, maaf ya, kita tak boleh refund. 😔 Apa yang boleh boss buat: 1️⃣ Gunakan baki yang ada untuk bermain dan cuba menang balik. 2️⃣ Boss perlu menang sekurang-kurangnya 30% dari modal sebelum boleh buat pengeluaran. 3️⃣ Contohnya, kalau transfer RM200, boss perlu menang RM60 dulu sebelum boleh withdraw RM260. Semoga banyak ONG dan HUAT lepas ni! Kalau ada soalan lain, boleh tanya dalam live chat ya boss! 😊🙏

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan top-up dalam aplikasi?

languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan top-up dalam aplikasi?

detailed.ms:
Salam boss! Kalau nak topup, boleh ikut langkah ini:

📌 Min Topup:
✅ ATM/Transfer (DuitNow/Instant Transfer) – Min RM10
✅ Fast Payment (FPX) – Min RM50 (lebih cepat & automatik)

📌 Cara Topup:
1️⃣ Pergi ke halaman topup dalam app.
2️⃣ Pilih kaedah topup (ATM/Transfer atau Fast Payment).
3️⃣ Masukkan jumlah topup & upload resit (jika guna ATM/Transfer).

Kalau ada pertanyaan lain, boleh roger kami di live chat ya boss! 😊🙏

question.text: How can I top up my BLM account using Fast Payment (FPX) and what should I do if the top-up does not reflect after a few minutes?

languages.en: How can I top up my BLM account using Fast Payment (FPX) and what should I do if the top-up does not reflect after a few minutes?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top-up akaun BLM saya menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX) dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up tidak muncul selepas beberapa minit?

detailed.en: To top-up using Fast Payment (FPX), follow these steps: 1. Open the app and go to the top-up page. 2. Select 'Fast Payment (FPX)' and choose your bank. 3. Enter the top-up amount (Min RM50) and confirm the transaction. 4. Wait for 1-3 minutes, the system will automatically verify. If after 3 minutes your RM150 top-up has not reflected, please send the complete FPX receipt to live chat for verification. If you have any issues, feel free to reply!
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka aplikasi & pergi ke halaman top-up. 2. Pilih 'Fast Payment (FPX)' dan pilih bank anda. 3. Masukkan jumlah top-up (Min RM50) dan sahkan transaksi. 4. Tunggu 1-3 minit, sistem akan mengesahkan secara automatik. Jika selepas 3 minit top-up RM150 anda masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit FPX lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk balas ya!

question.text: What are the guidelines for making transfers or top-ups to avoid issues?

languages.en: What are the guidelines for making transfers or top-ups to avoid issues?
languages.ms: Apakah garis panduan untuk membuat pemindahan atau top-up untuk mengelakkan masalah?
languages.cn: 为了避免问题，进行转账或充值的指南是什么？

detailed.en: For future transactions, please use your own bank account that matches the name registered in this ID for any transfers or top-ups. This is important to avoid any issues and ensure the verification process runs smoothly. Thank you very much for your cooperation and understanding!

question.text: Apa yang perlu buat jika terlupa letak ID JOKER masa transfer?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu buat jika terlupa letak ID JOKER masa transfer?
languages.cn: 如果我在转账时忘记填写JOKER ID该怎么办？

detailed.en: Don't worry if you forget to include the JOKER ID during the transfer! Here’s what you need to do: Ensure that the transaction receipt is complete and clear. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app as usual. Wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to verify the transaction. For next time, make sure to write the JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' section so that the system can verify it faster. If you have any issues or need assistance, feel free to contact us via live chat!

Muat naik resit ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi seperti biasa. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Untuk lain kali, pastikan anda menulis ID JOKER di ruangan 'Recipient Reference' supaya sistem boleh mengesahkannya dengan lebih cepat. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat!
detailed.cn: 如果您在转账时忘记填写JOKER ID，请不要担心！您需要做的是：确保交易收据完整且清晰。像往常一样将收据上传到应用程序中的充值页面。等待3-10分钟以便系统验证交易。下次请确保在“收件人参考”部分写下JOKER ID，以便系统可以更快地验证。如果您有任何问题或需要帮助，请随时通过在线聊天与我们联系！

detailed.cn: 如果您之前可以转账到Maybank，但现在无法切换到HLB，可能是所选银行账户存在问题。请确保输入的HLB账户号码正确，并检查平台是否存在技术问题。如果问题仍然存在，请尝试进行小额转账以测试账户的功能。如果您遇到进一步的问题，请通过在线聊天与我们联系，提供更多详细信息。

question.text: I have already transferred but my balance has not been updated in the app. What should I do?
variations: I have transferred but it hasn't reflected.
My balance is not updated after the transfer.

languages.en: I have already transferred but my balance has not been updated in the app. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya sudah transfer tetapi baki saya belum dikemas kini dalam aplikasi. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have transferred, please ensure you: 1️⃣ Upload the receipt in the top-up section of the app. 2️⃣ Check the status in Wallet → Transaction History. 3️⃣ If it shows 'Pending', the system is processing. 4️⃣ Do not upload the same receipt twice. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't updated, please contact me here for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah transfer, pastikan anda: 1️⃣ Muat naik resit di bahagian topup dalam aplikasi. 2️⃣ Semak status di Wallet → Transaction History. 3️⃣ Jika menunjukkan 'Pending', sistem sedang memproses. 4️⃣ Jangan muat naik resit yang sama dua kali. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dikemas kini, sila hubungi saya di sini untuk bantuan lanjut.
